        <updateDate>2026-04-06T17:02:31Z</updateDate>
        <text><![CDATA[<p>This resolution expresses condolences to the families, friends, and loved ones of the victims of UPS Airlines flight 2976, which crashed in Louisville, Kentucky,&nbsp;on November 4, 2025.</p><p>The resolution&nbsp;also</p><ul><li>honors those who lost their lives, and</li><li>commends the first responders and emergency personnel.</li></ul>]]></text>
      </summary>
    </summaries>
